name: tronie 06052021
description:
The "tronie" is a study of expression, type and physiognomy of an unknown or even non-existing person, popular among Dutch and Flemish painters during the Golden Age.
I generate them assisted by A.I. by uploading classic and contemporary works to a generative adversarial network | artist: Bas Uterwijk (ganbrood) | medium: PNG, 2677x3200 pixels | original creation date: June 5, 2021
